OL,3,CFormer priest accused of assault says
OL,4,Che was 'direct by today's standard'
OL,6,FA former priest accused of assaulting
OL,7,Fwomen in an alleged cult church group
OL,8,Fin Sheffield has said that he led "on
OL,9,Fconsensus" and denied manipulation.
OL,11,FChristopher Brain, 68, from Wilmslow
OL,12,Fin Cheshire, was leader of the
OL,13,Fevangelical movement the Nine O'Clock
OL,14,FService (NOS), as part of the Church
OL,15,Fof England, in Sheffield between 1986
OL,16,Fand 1995.
OL,18,FBrain denies one count of rape and 36
OL,19,Fcounts of indecent assault between
OL,20,F1981 and 1995 against 13 women.
