OL,4,Che was 'direct by today's standard'
OL,6,FProsecutors say NOS became a cult
OL,7,Fwhere Brain abused his position to
OL,8,Fsexually assault a "staggering number"
OL,9,Fof women followers, exerting control
OL,10,Fover their lives and ostracising them
OL,11,Ffrom friends and family.
OL,13,FOn Monday 4 August, Brain told jurors
OL,14,Fat Inner London Crown Court that he
OL,15,Fhad a leading role in a group in
OL,16,FSheffield from the early 1980s.
OL,18,FDefence lawyer Iain Simkin KC asked
OL,19,FBrain if he attempted to indoctrinate
OL,20,Fthose in the group.
