OL,6,FThe NOS began in 1986, and the
OL,7,Fdefendant said it had a "team
OL,8,Fstructure" but that he led the
OL,9,Fcongregation. He spoke about leading
OL,10,Fthe design of the worship, choosing
OL,11,Fthe music, songs and lighting.
OL,13,FBrain said he "rarely" stood at the
OL,14,Ffront of worships and instead played
OL,15,Fmore of a "producer" role.
OL,17,FMr Simkin asked Brain if he was a
OL,18,F"controlling maniac" who ran a cult
OL,19,Ffor his own ends. The defendant said
OL,20,Fhe was not.
