OL,6,FMr Simkin asked the defendant if he
OL,7,Fmade members "obey" or if he turned
OL,8,Fthem into "robots" for his "sexual
OL,9,Fdesires", which he denied.
OL,11,FAsked if members could work, the
OL,12,Fdefendant said: "Yes of course. Some
OL,13,Fof them had normal jobs."
OL,15,FMr Simkin asked Brain about his
OL,16,Fleadership style, to which the
OL,17,Fdefendant said: "I think most of the
OL,18,Ftime I worked on consensus, at the
OL,19,Ftime that's what I thought was most
OL,20,Fconsiderate, making sure you take
OL,21,Feverybody with you."
